  "detailed_description": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793690/extras/Final_Assault_Hero_Art_small_02.png?t=1554759654\" ><br><strong><i>Final Assault </i></strong>is a WWII themed Action Strategy Game built from the ground up to capitalize on the power of VR. Tower over the battlefield as war rages around you in 360 degrees. Final Assault focuses on the combat, removing base building and resource gathering and putting you into the battle quickly. Command jeeps, tanks, artillery and aircraft in massive ground to air battles. Execute air strikes and bombing runs as you advance your troops towards enemy territory. Control your units by drawing paths for precise, direct combat. Strategic decisions have consequences that require quick thinking and fast VR reflexes. This new approach to classic RTS gaming utilizes compelling and immersive game-play that can only exist in VR. Jump into the combat. <strong><i>Fight the battle, Win the War!</i></strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cross-Platform Support- Fully support Oculus, HTC Vive and WMR. Future support for PSVR<br></li><li>Modes: Story Campaign and Skirmish, PVE and PVP<br></li><li>Movement: World drag<br></li><li>12 unique PvP maps<br></li><li>2 Starting Factions - USA &amp; Germany<br></li><li>6 different Divisions <br></li><li>Leader-boards and Achievements<br></li><li>Customization of Units, Flags and Player Avatars<br></li><li>Spectator cameras</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/793690/extras/Final_Assault_Hero_Art_small_02.png?t=1554759654\" ><br><strong><i>Final Assault </i></strong>is a WWII themed Action Strategy Game built from the ground up to capitalize on the power of VR. Tower over the battlefield as war rages around you in 360 degrees. Final Assault focuses on the combat, removing base building and resource gathering and putting you into the battle quickly. Command jeeps, tanks, artillery and aircraft in massive ground to air battles. Execute air strikes and bombing runs as you advance your troops towards enemy territory. Control your units by drawing paths for precise, direct combat. Strategic decisions have consequences that require quick thinking and fast VR reflexes. This new approach to classic RTS gaming utilizes compelling and immersive game-play that can only exist in VR. Jump into the combat. <strong><i>Fight the battle, Win the War!</i></strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Cross-Platform Support- Fully support Oculus, HTC Vive and WMR. Future support for PSVR<br></li><li>Modes: Story Campaign and Skirmish, PVE and PVP<br></li><li>Movement: World drag<br></li><li>12 unique PvP maps<br></li><li>2 Starting Factions - USA &amp; Germany<br></li><li>6 different Divisions <br></li><li>Leader-boards and Achievements<br></li><li>Customization of Units, Flags and Player Avatars<br></li><li>Spectator cameras</li></ul>",
