  "reviews": "\u201cFinal Assault \u2013 War Is Hell\u2026Ishly Good Fun Hours and hours of high-quality entertainment.\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.vrfocus.com/2019/03/preview-final-assault-war-is-hell-ishly-good-fun/?fbclid=IwAR0DzyolPeIfhF9021LXpSXFGVycPezftSD2ucKz07AeLAL3B23ChBThNP0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >VRFocus</a><br><br>\u201cI was blown away by how well Phaser Lock Interactive\u2019s VR real time strategy game, Final Assault, captured all the fun of a real time strategy game while streamlining all the messy bits, creating an immersive virtual tabletop wargame\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://pixelkin.org\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Pixelkin</a><br><br>\u201cFinal Assault is a legitimate opportunity for compelling competitive VR&quot;\u201d<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.dailyesports.gg/final-assault-is-a-legitimate-opportunity-for-compelling-competitive-vr/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >DailyEsports</a><br>",
